item.title: LupinStory
item.description: LupinStory I tried to recreate a funny little Maplestory game that I played as a little kid. It was called MonkeyStory. Maplestory was a big part of my childhood, I played a ton of it with my brother and I remember revolving a lot a lot of time around it.
